span class=\"cit-name-given-names\">A. R.</span></span>,</li>\n                    <li><span class=\"cit-auth\"><span class=\"cit-name-surname\">Silveira</span> <span class=\"cit-name-given-names\">E.</span></span>,</li>\n                    <li><span class=\"cit-auth\"><span class=\"cit-name-surname\">Baquero</span> <span class=\"cit-name-given-names\">F.</span></span>,</li>\n                    <li><span class=\"cit-auth\"><span class=\"cit-name-surname\">Peixe</span> <span class=\"cit-name-given-names\">L.</span></span>,</li>\n                    <li><span class=\"cit-auth\"><span class=\"cit-name-surname\">Roberts</span> <span class=\"cit-name-given-names\">A. P.</span></span>,</li>\n                    <li><span class=\"cit-auth\"><span class=\"cit-name-surname\">Coque</span> <span class=\"cit-name-given-names\">T. M.</span></span></li>\n                  </ol><cite><strong>(</strong><span class=\"cit-pub-date\">2012</span><strong>).</strong> <span class=\"cit-article-title\">Different genetic supports for the <em>tet</em>(S) gene in enterococci</span>. <abbr class=\"cit-jnl-abbrev\">Antimicrob Agents Chemother</abbr> <span class=\"cit-vol\">56</span> (in <span class=\"cit-pub-id-sep cit-pub-id-doi-sep\">press</span><span class=\"cit-pub-id cit-pub-id-doi\"><span class=\"cit-pub-id-scheme-doi\">doi:</span>10.1128/AAC.00758-12</span></cite>\n                </div>\n\n              </div>\n            </li>\n            <li>\n              <span class=\"ref-label ref-label-empty\"></span>\n              <div class=\"cit ref-cit ref-journal\" id=\"cit-158.Pt_11.2710.7\">\n                <div class=\"cit-metadata\">\n                  <ol class=\"cit-auth-list\">\n                    <li><span class=\"cit-auth\"><span class=\"cit-name-surname\">Palmieri</span> <span class=\"cit-name-given-names\">C.</span></span>,</li>\n                    <li><span class=\"cit-auth\"><span class=\"cit-name-surname\">Magi</span> <span class=\"cit-name-given-names\">G.</span></span